My little girl has been going to Pat a Cake since she was 1 & has loved it every week. Hayley is a g...reat teacher & manages to hold their attention for the whole class. The music is great & Hayley always has a smile on her face! Even I love going to the class & it's also a nice time to catch up with friends. There is always nice coffee & a surprise treat, which is a great touch as it gives the mum's chance to chat without interrupting the class. Lottie who is now 2 will be starting the new pre school sessions in September & I can't wait to see what Hayley has in store! 展开
